<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="rubbish-n">rubbish <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'rʌbɪʃ/    美 /'rʌbɪʃ/  </p>
<p>[U] (garbage)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-ame-trash">1.★ <strong>垃圾；废物 (AmE trash)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>collect rubbish 
收垃圾</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>废话；无聊的想法：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don’t <strong>talk rubbish</strong>! 
别说废话！</p></div></div>